  "text": "Before proposing our non-parametric estimator, we briefly describe existing estimators. [CITATION_1] describes what we refer to as the normal distributions partial AUC estimator (NDE), which assumes that the test results for diseased and non-diseased populations follow normal distributions with different means and variances. Maximum likelihood estimates of these parameters provide the ROC curve estimate, and numerical integration of it gives the partial AUC estimator:",
